Drawbacks of SDLC:
------------------
1. Developer Vs Operations --> Clashes between teams to deliver faster
2. Manual tasks --> Errors can be encountered frequently
3. Step-by-step manner --> The team that is handling the project is busy with their tasks, while the previous and next team are idle or they move to new tasks creating issues in the future while sharing the feedback
----------------------------------------------------------------------
----------------------------------------------------------------------
* To overcome these issues, Agile method was introduced *
